nmc-article alias: Cover having been cancelled by the insurance companies
nmc-article id: the risk of labour disputes and terrorist attacks in and on the buildings occupied by the Court of Auditors is now covered by the general budget of the European Union. The appropriations earmarked under this title therefore cover all expenditure incurred in repairing damage resulting from labour disputes and terrorist attacks.
amounts: This appropriation is intended to cover long-lease fees and other similar expenditure owed by the institution under lease/purchase contracts.
